articles.author: ABC News
articles.title: Elon Musk will move Tesla's headquarters to Texas in another blow for California business
articles.description: Housing affordability is mentioned by the company's chief executive as a big problem for operating in the Bay Area.
articles.content:
Tesla chief executive Elon Musk says he is moving his company headquarters from California to Texas, citing housing prices as a major issue for his employees.
